#. <CLT 04>砂浜に着いた。<CLT>
msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Here we are at the rec room...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>どこまでも続く青い海、そして白い砂浜。<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>実に南国らしいロケーションだ。<CLT>
msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>There's all kinds of games and stuff to do in here.\n"
"Almost makes me feel like I'm not at school...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>俺たちの他に人影はないみたいだけど…<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>さてどうしようか？<CLT>
msgctxt "0003"
msgid "Wanna play Othello?"
msgstr ""

#. 焼こう！
msgctxt "0004"
msgid "Oh! Yeah, Othello's good stuff!"
msgstr ""

#. ボクも色が黒いのには憧れるんだけど
#. 肌が弱くてさ…
msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"I'm quite skilled at brain games, ya know. I'm gonna\n"
"push you to your limit!"
msgstr ""

#. それに紫外線がね…
#. 運が悪い方に作用しそうな気がしてちょっとね…
msgctxt "0006"
msgid "Let's play some pool."
msgstr ""

#. できればあまり積極的には焼かない方向の
#. 遊びにしてもらえると助かるよ。
msgctxt "0007"
msgid "Hrmmm..."
msgstr ""

#. 砂の城を作ろう！
msgctxt "0008"
msgid "Okay, you got it! Let's play!"
msgstr ""

#. いいね！
#. それなら比較的安全だよ！
msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"Let's begin with you explaining the rules to this\n"
"\"pool\" you speak of!"
msgstr ""

#. まぁきっと、完成間近で大きな波が来て
#. 流されるのは目に見えてるんだけど…
msgctxt "0010"
msgid "Have you ever made a ship in a bottle?"
msgstr ""

#. ボク、あまり何かをちゃんと
#. 無事に完成させられた事がないんだよね。
msgctxt "0011"
msgid "I'm not so good at detailed handiwork like that."
msgstr ""

#. でも、キミと一緒に作るなら
#. もしかして上手くいくかもしれない。
msgctxt "0012"
msgid ""
"I mean, it's such a small opening, and such a big\n"
"ship. It's..."
msgstr ""

#. よし、早速やってみよう！
msgctxt "0013"
msgid "It's impossible! There's no way it can be done!"
msgstr ""

#. 泳ごう！
msgctxt "0014"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 是非そうしたいところだけど…
msgctxt "0015"
msgid "Let's check our horoscope in the magazine."
msgstr ""

#. うーん…やっぱり波打ち際で遊ぶくらいに
#. しておいたほうがいいかもしれないよ。
msgctxt "0016"
msgid "Y-You believe in stuff like that!?"
msgstr ""

#. 突然高波が来たり、何故か局地的に
#. 大嵐になったりする事もあるから…
msgctxt "0017"
msgid "Pitiful, Makoto... Very pitiful!"
msgstr ""

#. ボクは運が良いから多分大丈夫だけど、
#. キミを巻き込んだら申し訳ないからね。
msgctxt "0018"
msgid "I mean really..."
msgstr ""

#. とりあえず釣ろうか
msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"I hate being manipulated by the stupid horoscopes they\n"
"put in these stupid magazines!"
msgstr ""

#. 釣りか…釣りはいいな。
#. 不測の事態が起こりにくいからね。
msgctxt "0020"
msgid "What kinds of magazines do you like?"
msgstr ""

#. よほど不安定な場所で釣らない限り、
#. 釣り竿が折れるか、大物が釣れるかの二択だし。
msgctxt "0021"
msgid ""
"Oh, I don't read magazines. A nice, thick newspaper is\n"
"all I need!"
msgstr ""

#. あ、たまにものすごくわけのわからないものが
#. 釣れる事もあるけどね！
msgctxt "0022"
msgid "Is that a dartboard?"
msgstr ""

#. よし、じゃあどっちがより大きいのを釣るか
#. 勝負しようか！
msgctxt "0023"
msgid ""
"Ah yes, darts. I actually tried my hand at it with\n"
"Celeste already."
msgstr ""

#. もちろん、魚以外でも可だからね！
msgctxt "0024"
msgid ""
"When do you go for more points, and when do you give\n"
"up? It's actually a pretty intellectual game!"
msgstr ""

#. とりあえず脱ごうか
msgctxt "0025"
msgid ""
"Of course, the game ended in a clean sweep for\n"
"Celeste..."
msgstr ""

#. それはつまり…
msgctxt "0026"
msgid "Apparently I still lack the proper diligence!"
msgstr ""

#. ボクと一緒に海に入るって事かな？
msgctxt "0027"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. だとしたら色々と危ないから
#. やめておいた方がいいと思うよ。
msgctxt "0028"
msgid "Kinda boring here, huh...?"
msgstr ""

#. ボクの裸が見たいだけなら
#. 別に構わないんだけど。
msgctxt "0029"
msgid ""
"There's no such thing as boredom in life! If you're\n"
"bored, that means you're wasting time!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>構わないのかよ…<CLT>
msgctxt "0030"
msgid "You're the one who invited me here!"
msgstr ""

#. とりあえず走ろうか
msgctxt "0031"
msgid ""
"If you're just standing around with all this spare\n"
"time, it would've been better to spend it studying!"
msgstr ""

#. うーん、ボクはパスするよ。
msgctxt "0032"
msgid "I'm not sure about any of these games..."
msgstr ""

#. キミは好きなだけ犬のように
#. 走り回ってくるといいと思うよ。
msgctxt "0033"
msgid "Hahaha! You've got a point there!"
msgstr ""

#. スイカでも割るか
msgctxt "0034"
msgid ""
"This rec room is more of a hassle than it's worth,\n"
"that's for sure."
msgstr ""

#. スイカ割りか…やった事ないな…
msgctxt "0035"
msgid "Now let's go to the library and hit the books!"
msgstr ""

#. やめておいた方が無難なのは
#. わかってるけど、でも…
msgctxt "0036"
msgid ""
"Plant that butt, arch that back, put your head down\n"
"and get to studying!"
msgstr ""

#. 目隠しをして凶器を持ったボクが
#. いったいどんな不運に見舞われるのか…
msgctxt "0037"
msgid "Hope's Peak really is amazing..."
msgstr ""

#. そう考えると、楽しみ過ぎてゾクゾクするよ！
msgctxt "0038"
msgid "Mm, indeed. It's a most excellent facility."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>そこまでは考えてなかったな…<CLT>
msgctxt "0039"
msgid ""
"A room like this is completely unnecessary for a\n"
"positively sacred school like this. Am I right!?"
msgstr ""

#. 貝殻を拾うか
msgctxt "0040"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like nobody's here right now.\n"
"What should we do?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
